It's just a bit hot though.

19
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:31,720
Too hot.

20
00:03:34,079 --> 00:03:35,760
I need to take this call.

21
00:03:36,160 --> 00:03:37,360
You two take the drone

22
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:39,800
and fly it further out to get more exterior shots.

23
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:40,480
Okay.

24
00:03:43,240 --> 00:03:44,640
Can Fatty fly it?

25
00:03:45,880 --> 00:03:49,640
Champion of the No. 2 Elementary School remote control car competition.

26
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:51,840
As long as it doesn't crash, we're good.

27
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:56,360
Can you handle it?

28
